OL,3,CWelsh tourist being held in
OL,4,C'horrendous conditions' after being
OL,5,Cdetained in US
OL,7,FThe parents of a Welsh tourist
OL,8,Fdetained in the US have told ITV News
OL,9,Ftheir daughter is being held in
OL,10,F'horrendous conditions', after she was
OL,11,Faccused of violating her visa. They
OL,12,Fspoke to ITV News reporter Charlie
OL,13,FFrost.
OL,15,FRebecca Burke, 28, an artist from
OL,16,FMonmouthshire, had embarked on what
OL,17,Fshould have been the trip of a
OL,18,Flifetime, four months of travelling
OL,19,Fand backpacking across North America
OL,20,Fand then Canada.
