OL,3,CWelsh tourist being held in
OL,4,C'horrendous conditions' after being
OL,5,Cdetained in US
OL,7,FShe had a tourist visa for the trip,
OL,8,Fleaving for the US on the 7th of
OL,9,FJanuary. She flew from New York to
OL,10,FPortland, Oregon, where she spent time
OL,11,Fwith a host family, helping with
OL,12,Fhousehold chores in exchange for
OL,13,Faccommodation.
OL,15,FAt the end of February she travelled
OL,16,Fto Seattle, with plans to travel to
OL,17,FVancouver in Canada to stay with
OL,18,Fanother family.
