OL,5,Cdetained in US
OL,7,FBut when she reached the US-Canadian
OL,8,Fborder, Canadian authorities denied
OL,9,Fher entry, concerned she was trying to
OL,10,Fwork illegally.
OL,12,FOfficials said she needed a working
OL,13,Fvisa and sent Ms. Burke back to the US
OL,14,F- where she was then taken by homeland
OL,15,Fsecurity to a large detention centre.
OL,17,FThe 28 year-old's now been in the
OL,18,Fdetention centre for 2 weeks.
