OL,7,FBecky's father, Paul Burke told ITV
OL,8,FNews: "They called homeland security
OL,9,Fwho took her in handcuffs, literally
OL,10,Fin handcuffs, to a detention centre in
OL,11,FTacoma in Washington State."
OL,13,FHer mum Angela Burke added: "They
OL,14,Factually made a point of saying to
OL,15,Fher, it'll only be a couple of days
OL,16,Fand this isn't a jail - but I beg to
OL,17,Fdiffer."
