OL,7,F"Well, it's obviously not a couple of
OL,8,Fdays, so we quickly learned that and
OL,9,Fwhen Becky describes the conditions to
OL,10,Fus its the almost perfect definition
OL,11,Fof a jail." Paul told us.
OL,13,FHe added: "She's had all her
OL,14,Fpossessions taken off her. She's had
OL,15,Fto change from her own clothes into a
OL,16,Fprison jumpsuit, she shares a cell
OL,17,Fwith another woman, she's allowed out
OL,18,Fin the yard for an hour every day."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
