OL,7,FAndrea said: "She was totally
OL,8,Fdistraught at first, and I think she's
OL,9,Fjust dealing with it on a one day
OL,10,Fbasis."
OL,12,F"It's hard to explain, you're going
OL,13,Fthrough the motions of daily activity
OL,14,Fbut its like you're walking through
OL,15,Ftreacle sometimes, or even life stands
OL,16,Fstill, we're watching ourselves doing
OL,17,Fstuff but life stopped 2 weeks ago.'"
OL,19,F"She just wants to come home, and
OL,20,Fthat's all that we want, is for her to
OL,21,Fcome home."
